        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h6>Wind Arrow Colors:</h6>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><span style="color: #4dabf7;">‚û§</span> <strong>Light Blue:</strong> 0-2 m/s (Calm)</li>
                <li><span style="color: #1c7ed6;">‚û§</span> <strong>Blue:</strong> 2-4 m/s (Light breeze)</li>
                <li><span style="color: #ffd43b;">‚û§</span> <strong>Yellow:</strong> 4-8 m/s (Moderate breeze)</li>
                <li><span style="color: #ff922b;">‚û§</span> <strong>Orange:</strong> 8-10 m/s (Fresh breeze)</li>
                <li><span style="color: #e03131;">‚û§</span> <strong>Red:</strong> 10+ m/s (Strong wind)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-muted">
        <small>
            ‚Ä¢ Map updates every 2 seconds with new rover data<br/>
